The paper proposes a structured approach to image retrieval using a description logic and semantic indexing. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of reasoning services for retrieval, classification, and subsumption, which are common topics in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses experiments carried out on a testbed of images, indicating a focus on Multimedia (cs.MM).
